        <item>
            <title>大陆男香港机场遗失八达通，惊叹贼人 2 日仅用 6.6</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/chinese-man-lost-octopus-in-airport/life-tech/epayment/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chinese-man-lost-octopus-in-airport</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/chinese-man-lost-octopus-in-airport/life-tech/epayment/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 07:07:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[八达通]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299469</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港国际机场近日发生一宗八达通遗失事件。一名来自中国大陆的男子在机场八达通增值机遗留八达通，卡内余额为 28 元，仅 5 分钟后折返已不翼而飞。两天后他透过香港朋友报失，发现退款余额达 21.4 元，显示贼人仅用了 6.6 元。此事在网上引起热议，网民对贼人用量之少感到意外。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299471" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1040g00831f4rsu4hmm0-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1040g00831f4rsu4hmm0-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1040g00831f4rsu4hmm0.jpeg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/1040g00831f4rsu4hmm0-144x144.jpeg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67d841da000000001c0022bf?app_platform=android&amp;ignoreEngage=true&amp;app_version=8.72.0&amp;share_from_user_hidden=true&amp;xsec_source=app_share&amp;type=normal&amp;xsec_token=CB4TaHqBT-ruO1omFrhUkwzDH5UmpqWSfdtCMgyN5HQmM=&amp;author_share=1&amp;xhsshare=CopyLink&amp;shareRedId=ODlFNzZKNE82NzUyOTgwNjg6OTlFSTZB&amp;apptime=1742345099">xhs</a></p><p>该中国男子早前在香港交流时申请了一张实名八达通。事发当日，他从国外抵港，计划转乘巴士回中国，在机场增值时因机器故障放弃操作，却忘取八达通。5 分钟后返回发现卡已失窃。两天后报失，退款显示贼人仅消费 6.6 元，他惊讶表示：「捡到八达通拿去用的贼挺节俭。」</p><p>据八达通公司资料，报失个人八达通需扣除 50 元费用，包括手续费及卡成本，从按金中扣减。补领个人八达通需付港币 70 元，其中 50 元为新卡的按金；20 元为补领新卡的手续费。失主可按以报失八达通。成功报失后，系统会提供一个报失编号作日后跟进纪录之用，报失指示将不能取消。客户只需承担成功报失后 3 小时内之损失。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299472" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032612923-694x457.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="457" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032612923-694x457.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032612923.jpg 848w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/consumer/customer-service/faq/customer-service/lost-octopus.html">octopus</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://scontent-atl3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/41068572_2434955366515393_7050688080562356224_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;ccb=1-7&amp;_nc_sid=127cfc&amp;_nc_ohc=FGJ8YRMb8u4Q7kNvgFjSOFM&amp;_nc_oc=AdmNy1sK4Ms3zL1xAJeT46NPXA4FOJMG4qfvc6QBU3Lwd0OC86X5iqW-dVhl6EZ8N-I&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-atl3-2.xx&amp;_nc_gid=3funl-b5h0Cgu0lC8fF4rg&amp;oh=00_AYGZeSCQun3Yl3rNXjKqIkZJT9igyij24BikYPsKl0t9Gg&amp;oe=680B0D84">MTR Service@Facebook</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.xiaohongshu.com/explore/67d841da000000001c0022bf?app_platform=android&amp;ignoreEngage=true&amp;app_version=8.72.0&amp;share_from_user_hidden=true&amp;xsec_source=app_share&amp;type=normal&amp;xsec_token=CB4TaHqBT-ruO1omFrhUkwzDH5UmpqWSfdtCMgyN5HQmM=&amp;author_share=1&amp;xhsshare=CopyLink&amp;shareRedId=ODlFNzZKNE82NzUyOTgwNjg6OTlFSTZB&amp;apptime=1742345099">xhs</a>、<a href="https://www.octopus.com.hk/tc/consumer/customer-service/faq/customer-service/lost-octopus.html">八达通</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
